			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">Beijing three-step: China denies, deflects and dissembles on Xinjiang</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/michael-clarke">
							Michael Clarke
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						The UN human rights report has exposed China’s hollow propaganda claims – but won’t stop them.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/2022-09/GettyImages-1232456228.jpg?itok=jk-Eqbl7" alt="The UN report vindicates what Uyghur advocacy organisations, human rights NGOs scholars have argued for years (Justin Tallis/AFP via Getty Images)">
              <div class="article-save-btn">
          
        </div>
      							<div class="article-main-image-caption">
					The UN report vindicates what Uyghur advocacy organisations, human rights NGOs scholars have argued for years (Justin Tallis/AFP via Getty Images)
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="clearfix">
			<div class="txt-center pv-md">
				<span class="txt-muted">
					Published 9 Sep 2022&nbsp;
				</span>

